data.description:
This beautiful, private two bedroom corner unit features an open concept with an eat-in kitchen and large family room. The unit backs up to the greenbelt where you can sit out on your gated patio and enjoy the shade from the large mature trees. Brand new wood-style luxury vinyl flooring in kitchen, family and hallways and new carpet in bedrooms. The bathroom features a walk in tub/shower.  There's an extra storage unit on the third floor as well as a detached one car garage. Laundry is available in the building and residents sign up for a weekly time. This unit offers so much potential - keep it as is or make it your own and build up equity! 

Windsor Gardens is a 55+ community full of amenities -a huge community center with an indoor pool, outdoor pool, hot tub, fitness center, 9 hole golf course, restaurant/bar and auditorium for events. The community center hosts many events and clubs for residents. There are multiple RTD bus stops throughout and quick access to I-225 making it a breeze to get around town! For the outdoor lover, Windsor Gardens connects up with the Highline Canal trail for miles of walking and biking. Close to Common Grounds golf course, Lowry Town Center and Boulevard One restaurants and shops. The HOA includes security patrol and 24 hour community response team.
